md:
giải nghĩa từ "import" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ trái nghĩa.

* Import (verb) - Nhập khẩu (to bring goods or services into a country from another country)
	+ Example: The company imports coffee from Brazil.
	+ Related words: export, trade, shipment
	+ Antonyms: export, ban

* Import (noun) - Hàng nhập khẩu (goods or services brought into a country from another country)
	+ Example: The import of foreign cars has increased significantly.
	+ Related words: export, trade, shipment
	+ Antonyms: export, domestic product

* Import (verb) - Nhập vào (to bring something into a computer system or program)
	+ Example: You need to import the data into the spreadsheet.
	+ Related words: export, upload, download
	+ Antonyms: export, delete

* Import (noun) - Sự nhập vào (the act of bringing something into a computer system or program)
	+ Example: The import of the new software took several hours.
	+ Related words: export, upload, download
	+ Antonyms: export, deletion
